title: Best black walnut cake
ingredients: ['110g butter, softened', '110g margarine, softened', '325g caster sugar', '350g plain flour', '1 teaspoon salt', '2 teaspoons baking powder', '3 eggs', '270ml milk', '1 teaspoon vanilla extract', '1 teaspoon black walnut extract', '120g chopped black walnuts']
